    Class Description
    GuildBanEventResponse
    This is a generic object representing all guild ban events.
    GuildEmojiUpdateResponse
    The response when the emoji list for a guild updates.
    GuildMemberAddEventResponse
    This is sent when a new member joins a guild
    GuildMemberChunkEventResponse
    This is returned when requesting additional guild members from a "large" guild.
    GuildMemberRemoveEventResponse
    This response is received when a user leaves a guild
    GuildMemberUpdateEventResponse
    This event is received when a member is updated in a guild.
    GuildRoleDeleteEventResponse
    This is received when a role was deleted.
    GuildRoleEventResponse
    This is received when a role is created or updated in a guild.
    MessageDeleteBulkEventResponse
    This is received when a bot bulk deletes
    MessageDeleteEventResponse
    This response is received when a message is deleted
    PresenceUpdateEventResponse
    This is received when a user's presence changes
    ReactionEventResponse
    Response when reactions are added or removed on a message.
    TypingEventResponse
    A response sent when a user starts typing
    UserUpdateEventResponse
    This is received when a user updates his/her account info
